esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Behold Khunzar-ri`s Betrayal',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Senche-raht Statue, Battle-Bound',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => '\"Oh, yes! I`ve seen legionaries stand their ground against a battle-bonded Khajiit pair. Never seen one survive the experience, but you`ve got to respect anyone who faces a Senche-raht and their chosen battlemate.\"\n—Nallangaer, Vinedusk Ranger',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'You have claimed a share of the Dragon`s Treasure Trove. Place it in your home, and show off your hard-earned riches.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Behold Khunzar-ri`s Guile',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Place on the Altar of Guile in the Hall of the Lunar Champion to unlock a long-forgotten corner of Moongrave Fane.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Statuette: Auri-El and Xarxes',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'A miniature statue of Auri-El and Xarxes, based on the statues in the Monastery of Serene Harmony in Shimmerene.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Statuette: Senche-raht',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'A miniature statue of a Senche-raht Khajiit and its chosen battlemate.',
