esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Place on the Altar of Ambition in the Hall of the Lunar Champion to unlock a portal to Khunzar-ri`s childhood home.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Statuette: Auri-El, Aldmer King',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'A miniature statue of Auri-El, chief deity of the Aldmeri pantheon, with an eagle.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Statuette: Boethra, Orkha-Bane',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'A miniature statue of Syrabane, an Aldmeri god-ancestor of magic.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Exquisitely designed, this warm-hued tapestry of Blackwood serves as both an art piece and a practical guide to the region.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'A painting by Vaudrie Barthel, well-known for her landscapes and scenes depicting life and nature in the Systres Isles.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Statuette: Baron-Admiral Olo',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'A miniature statue of Bendu Olo, Baron-Admiral of the All Flags Navy, as sculpted in High Isle.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'You may place the Chronometer in your home. Watching the dial spin causes local perception of time to shift. Until the Chronometer is disturbed, time stands still. Enjoy Sotha Sil`s morning sun, Almalexia`s mid-day mercy, or the star-spun night of Vivec.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'The light of dawn caresses the spires of Bal Foyen as a trader and their travel-burdened guar arrive at this Dark Elf sanctum by the sea.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'A miniature version of the \"Thirty-Fourth Sermon\" statue, carved by the people of Necrom.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Statuette: Yokudan War-Scholar',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Stories claim High Elves and Goblins once traded peacefully at King`s Haven Pass. After relations between the two soured, the Coral-Splitter Goblins claimed the area as their own.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Painting: 10-Year Anniversary',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'A painting representing Carapace Caverns, a bismuth-veined cave now plagued by an ancient undead curse.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Statuette: Roaring Cathay-Raht',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'A miniature statue of a Cathay-Raht roaring at foes.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Statuette: Defending Tojay-Raht',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'A miniature statue of a well-trained Tojay-Raht, who guards against all foes.',
