esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Biro-dar^M',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Don`t let Biro-dar`s appearance deceive you! He`s not your average scholar. In fact, he makes for an entertaining and trouble-prone guest. After adding Biro-dar to your home, you can set him on a path, plus you and your visitors can speak with him.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Son of Jorunn the Skald-King, Prince Irnskar often feels as if he lives in his father`s shadow. Hoping for a respite, he came to visit you. After adding Prince Irnskar to your home, you can set him on a path, plus you and your visitors can speak with him.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Adusa-daro^F',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Adusa-daro lives by a code of honor, vigilance, and restraint—the latter being of particular concern for a vampire. Will you invite her in? After adding Adusa-daro to your home, you can set her on a path, plus you and your visitors can speak with her.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Makes-Many-Soups^F',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'A chef of many soups, but perhaps only one at a time, the Argonian Makes-Many-Soups seeks to add her culinary creativity to your abode. After adding Makes-Many-Soups to your home, you can set her on a path, plus you and your visitors can speak with her.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'The long-suffering Stibbons, Lady Laurent`s servant, needs a break. He chose to seek you out, desperate for the peace your home provides. After adding Stibbons to your home, you can set him on a path, plus you and your visitors can speak with him.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Erilthel`s quest to become Lady Twilight, Tamriel`s greatest thief, brought her to your door until her teacher, Seeks-the-Dark, finds her again. After adding Erilthel to your home, you can set her on a path, plus you and your visitors can speak with her.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Relic-Apprentice Marafar^f',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Caska the Senche-raht serves as the first mate on The Perfect Pounce, and she loves time off to pursue other interests—perhaps in your house! After adding Caska to your home, you can set her on a path, plus you and your visitors can speak with her.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'No job is too small for this Pahmar-raht resistance fighter. That said, he needs a place to rest before his next efforts against his oppressors. After adding J`baanluk to your home, you can set him on a path, plus you and your visitors can speak with him.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Sharp-as-Night^M',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Solitary mercenary Sharp-as-Night isn`t used to company, but if you invite him into your home, this warden will leave his icy demeanor at the door. Mostly. Talk to him to hear his unfiltered thoughts, or set him on a path to let him wander your estate.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Azandar al-Cybiades is a consummate researcher and peerless arcanist. Just ask him! After adding Azandar to your home, you can set him on a path. You and your guests can also talk to him. Trust us, he`s got plenty to say.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'This Orc mercenary usually keeps busy, but now he wants some actual quiet time. Not to reflect, though—his well-used gear needs some attention. After adding Skordo to your home, you can set him on a path, plus you and your visitors can speak with him.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Some may call Tanlorin a rabble-rouser or rapscallion. They much prefer being called a friend. After adding Tanlorin to your home, you can set them on a path to wander. You can also speak with them. But be warned, they`re a bit of a talker.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'name' => 'Zerith-var',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Though far from his own time, Zerith-var is sure to brighten any living space with his thoughtful observations and warm company. After adding Zerith to your home, you and guests can speak to him. You can also let him wander by setting him on a path.',
esoCollectibleData.php:										'desc' => 'Self-proclaimed expert adventurer and prolific author Narsis Dren needs some time away from his exploits to write his next thrilling book. After adding Narsis to your home, you can set him on a path, plus you and your visitors can speak with him.',
