esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Zhasim, a Khajiit raised by Orcs in Wrothgar, came to Southern Elsweyr to help his uncle get his shipment of gourmet moon-sugar to market in Rimmen. But Zhasim and his guard Maezi were robbed and his cat Winks ran away.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I've come upon <<1>>, a sun-baked wanderer. He inhabits a murky oasis near Tu'whacca's Throne. The wanderer seems to be speaking in fables regarding Sep's Hunger and a pearl.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Urgarlag Chief-bane of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore Castle Thorn.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Urgarlag Chief-bane of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore Bedlam Veil.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Inside a broken tower, I found a wounded woman named Imwyn Frost-Tree. She told me of a powerful symbol of her faith, the Sigil of Nature's Accord.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Baron Winoc tells me that Camlorn is in an uneasy state of truce between his Hands of Northmoor and the Magis Order. He is unsure where public opinion lies, and is too high-profile to ask around himself. He's asked me to ask around for him.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Razum-dar asked for my help with a mission to stop a pirate captain named Redblade from raising an armada.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Numani-Rasi of the Urshilaku Ashlander tribe has requested that I explore the ruins of the Daedric shrine Yasammidan and gather as many historic relics as I can find.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Disheveled NPC asked me to find a magical tome and bring it back to him. He says when I find it, I should quickly deliver it to him - there's no telling the evils abound...",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Verandis believes Rada al-Saran has set his final plan in motion. He seeks my help to put a stop to the Gray Host once and for all.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Elder Scroll of Ni-Mohk",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Blood-Cursed Town",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The town of Crestshade has been subjected to a blood-curse that turned the townsfolk feral. While some refugees were able to escape to the south, the mayor remained behind to aid any survivors.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Queen's Emissary - Isque",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Queen's Emissary - Orrery",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Knarstygg and Dro-Dara have decided it would be wise to go to Wayrest until the bandits clear out of the plantation. Knarstygg is concerned that Murk-Watcher might not want to leave.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Inquisitor Blarae has seen Morholdt as well - he has attacked the Redoubt many times. Also, the failed ritual in Camlorn caused the number of undead attacking the Redoubt to greatly increase. They threaten to overrun the Redoubt and destroy Camlorn.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Spider Cult has come to Fungal Grotto. Members of the Fighters Guild, led by Defender Two-Blades, are determined to stop the Cult from raising an army of shadows that will destabilize the region.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A follower of Peryite, the Daedric Prince of Pestilence, has asked me to rescue his friend from the flu-ridden city of Orcrest.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>> believes the spirit of a long-dead mage may know the secret to imprisoning Balreth again. An Argonian scout named <<2>> has already left for Othrenis.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Queen's Emissary - Dusk",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Tervur Sadri, the co-owner of the Darkshade mine, wants me to help him find his partner, Selos, and get rid of the thugs who've displaced his miners.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Bolu of the Dead-Water tribe, which calls itself the Naga-Kur, wants me to go to Bok-Xul and accomplish the task he set before me.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Commander Lafavre has asked you to kill the bosses controlling the Halls of the Damned.\n- Nazgol the Undying\n- General Ripfang\n- Bone Colossus\n- Orutu\n- Anarose Direblood\n- Therion Direblood",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Riekrs have been raiding caravans throughout Wrothgar, plundering cargo and taking travelers prisoners. The Riekrs, led by King-Chief Edu, must be dealt with.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Mallari-Mora",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I've found the body of a hunter in the wilds. Nearby was a notice he dropped detailing a bounty on senche-tiger fangs.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Ascendant Magus stands revealed as Count Damard Dufort. He intends to lead the Ascendant Order in an attack on All Flags Islet. Lady Arabelle needs me to help save the alliance leaders-and the hope for peace.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Kassandra betrayed us-she claimed the sap-speaker's staff and set out after the Remnant on her own. I need to reach her before she takes the Remnant for herself.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I helped Abnur Tharn decode the Wrathstone tablet and determine the location of the hidden weapon. Now we need to travel to the Halls of Colossus and find it before his half-sister, Euraxia. Khamira has decided to go with us.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Blood-Splattered Shield",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met a Bosmer named Ongalion at the Falinesti Autumn Site. He's a tree-steward, helping to tend the site while the city is away.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Death Among the Dead-Water",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Naga-Kur, or Dead-Water tribe, has sentenced Kishi, a member of the tribe, to death for interfering in the rites of passage and saving a few young Nagas from certain death. One of the survivors asked if I could help Kishi.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Missir-Dadalit Egg Mine has been overrun with kwama. I've been hired to clear out the infestation to help re-balance the colony. I'm also required to defeat a large kwama warrior who guards the queen.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Huntmaster Sorim-Nakar of the Erabenimsun Ashlander tribe has given me a challenge. He wants me to hunt the deadly greater hive golem they call Writhing Sveeth.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Huntmaster Sorim-Nakar of the Erabenimsun Ashlander tribe has given me a challenge. He wants me to hunt the dangerous cliff strider they call Old Stomper.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The elderly job broker, Ri'hirr, urged me to defeat Sword Master Vhysradue-a peerless warrior who camps on the Hill of Shattered Swords.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Urgarlag Chief-bane of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore the Cauldron.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Forbidden Worship - Old Ver.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A glory-seeking Orc warrior asked me to help him gather ogre teeth for a trophy necklace from the battle. Why not?",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Squire Albec asked for help finding Sir Cadwell's trusted steed, Honor. The bantam guar is loose somewhere on Solstice. The would-be squire believes Cadwell will officially accept him upon Honor's safe return.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The owners of the Dro-Dara Plantation have lost everything. First ogres attacked, and now bandits. The plantation was owned by a group of retired adventurers. The thief, Janne, asked me to rescue the others.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Treasure-hunting pirates have disturbed the undead necromancers in <<1>>. Now the great seal that kept them trapped has been weakened and the necromancers may soon be free to threaten all of Hew's Bane.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Wayward Guardians need silver ore to coat their arms and armor in order to better fight against the Gray Host. Ardanir asked me to bring him some from the Dwarven ruins of Bthar-Zel.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Concordia Mercius of Cyrodilic Collections needs my help to stop Margus Derius and the Blackguards from obtaining the Golden Skull of Beela-Kaar.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "A King-Sized Problem",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Mim-Jasa, a priest of the Clutch of Nisswo, asked me to help perform last rites for the Shadowscales who were entombed in the cave long ago. Doing so will supposedly prevent a necromancer named Tumma-Maxath from using them for his own evil purposes.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Walks-Softly wants some more of my help with the situation involving his old friend, Anais Velmont. The letter he left indicates he's come up with a solution that he wants to run by me.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Though the Omen of Fear has been dealt with and Alcaire is free of its influence, Duke Nathaniel is concerned. He's asked me to go seek the counsel of a Spirit Warden named Muran-to see if he can explain what happened.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Mazza-Mirri, the last surviving member of the Hidden Moon Order, led me to an enchanted Moonlight Blade. The soul of an ancient Khajiiti warrior resides within. With this enchanted blade, and Vastarie's help, I may be able to stop Arum-Khal.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "So-and-so has asked that you do something cool. Won't you do something cool.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met a talking monkey in Sentinel. The monkey claims he's really an Orc and that he was tricked by a Khajiit potion-maker named Unishi. He wants to be changed back.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The hamlet of Moira's Hope has met with disaster. Bloodfiends fill the streets, and the few survivors that remain are trying desperately to stay alive. I agreed to help Adusa-daro provide aid and find out who is behind this attack.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "An Argonian named Walks-Under-Shadow asked me to retrieve something called the Nightwielder's Tome from Xi-Tsei. Retrieving the tome will help him perform the proper rites for a nisswo priest named Nesh-Tei who died trying to find it.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "With <<1>> dead-again-and the new Silvenar revealed, <<2>> asked me to head to <<3>> in <<4>>. The Aldmeri Dominion needs to prepare for the wedding between the Green Lady and the newly-discovered Silvenar.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Dagonists drugged Saraathu Tong operatives-along with other prisoners-and left them outside Taupezu Azzida's lair to be eaten. I need to give the prisoners the antidote and kill Taupezu Azzida before it's too late.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Safa al-Satakalaam, a priest of Satakal, is at odds with the Scaled Court. Three of her most powerful acolytes have deserted her to worship the Celestial Serpent. She wants me to punish these traitors and deny their power to the Scaled Court.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Dro-Dara asked me to talk to the warrior Knarstygg about abandoning the plantation.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Pash-Riha hasn't returned to town yet. She's still hunting a Covenant lieutenant. Seven-Bellies is concerned for her safety. He believes she may be hunting southwest of the town.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "After the ritual at Rawl'kha, I traveled to meet the Lunar Champions at the temple called Moonmont. Here I'm told the Dark Mane has holed up. After what it did to Mane Akkhuz-ri, we must destroy it.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Elder Scroll of Ni-Mohk",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Elder Scroll of Ni-Mohk",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Grand Warlord Dortene reports that the Elder Scroll of Ni-Mohk is now in enemy hands.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Battlereeve Urcelmo has asked that I meet with Razum-dar near the town of Mathiisen. Raz is apparently investigating more threads in the Veiled Heritance plot.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Nisuzi's Baandari clan needs oil from Darkpool Mine, but a flock of Mehrunes Dagon-worshipers took control of the cavern-blocking access to the oil with hordes of newly summoned Daedra.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Some law-abiding citizens have been meddling in the affairs of the Thieves Guild. The guild wants its pickpockets to teach the meddlers to mind their own business. I should look for ornaments, writings, or other oddities, but any treasures will do.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Back-Alley Murders",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>> asked me to help her recover relics that belonged to a Minotaur-hunter named Phalevon the Magnificent from the partially flooded depths of Undertow Cavern. Goblins and Minotaurs infest the cave.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Mezha-dro, a Khajiit servant of Meridia, asked for help sealing tears in Oblivion before more material from Tamriel falls through.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A Pact Mage named Sees-Many-Paths is examining the wards at Tormented Spire. She wants word sent to her egg-sister, Walks-in-Ash, that they are unstable.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Office of Divine Prosecution tasked me with killing Keelsplitter-a massive sea adder bred by the Sea Elves to hunt down High Elf ships. They also need me to recover intelligence logs from the ships Keelsplitter destroyed.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Prefect Antias asked me to re-light the flame atop Crown Point tower.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Lady Laurent and Stibbons have been hired by the House of Orsimer Glories to locate the shrine of Torug gro-Igron, which supposedly sits at the top of the mountain named Sorrow.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Divine Prosecution has tasked me to recover several blossoms of the Rose-Of-Archon flower, needed by Sapiarchs for their religious rites.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Stormy-Eyes seems to be recovering from the Dreamstride experience. King Jorunn and Prince Irnskar have gone ahead to Jorunn's Stand, a large encampment near Skuldafn.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found the Black Drake Villa, an old retreat for the Longhouse Emperors. The young adventurer Eveli Sharp-Arrow enlisted my help in searching for an important book hidden away inside.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "King Kurog of Orsinium struggles to defeat the Winterborn threat. His mother, Forge-Mother Alga, asked me to go to Frostbreak Fortress to aid the king.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Molag Bal seeks to destroy the Sublime Brazier-the key to rekindling the Dragonfires. Working with The Drake of Blades, Captain Caudex, and Father Egnatius, I must find a way to protect the Dragonfire Cathedral, and the brazier within.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Thane Oda Wolf-Sister believes that the Ternion monks might be able to heal King Jorunn. But their complex rituals require special components.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Trail of the Skin-Stealer",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Loremaster Celarus charged me with sealing more time breaches for the Psijic Order-this time in the Wood Elf homeland of Valenwood.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The pirate captain One-Eye and her crew reached Coldharbour through a whirlpool while searching for a legend called the Lost Fleet. They seem intent on investigating the nearby wrecks.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Dream-Walk Into Darkness",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Urgarlag Chief-bane of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore Exiled Redoubt.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Deetum-Jas's friend Leric has been having a terrible run of bad luck. He asked me to gather the components necessary to give him a proper Argonian blessing to change his fortune.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Rothalens have fallen on hard times. Sarisa has designs on Bar-Neeus's stall in the central market.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The peaceful Argonians of the Su-Zahleel tribe have been abducted and pressed into slavery by the Xit-Xaht-warrior fanatics that have been driven mad by their psychotic Hist. I must rescue the captives and put an end to the Xit-Xaht threat.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Numani-Rasi of the Urshilaku Ashlander tribe has requested that I explore the ruins of the Daedric shrine Maelkashishi and gather as many historic relics as I can find.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Jee-Lar's associates in Murkmire need accurate weather predictions to plan their expeditions. Luckily, a priestess of Kyne named Hodyette can supply them with accurate forecasts. I can find this mysterious prophetess in Eastmarch.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I received an invitation to go to Wrothgar and present myself to Forge-Mother Alga in the city of Orsinium. It appears that the Orcs of Wrothgar need some sort of assistance.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The influential Bright-Throat tribe broker alliances with their neighbors through a complex system of bonding rituals. It is a delicate time for the tribe and it seems that this season's preparations have been plagued by unforeseen complications.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I've discovered the Ember-Eye's plans for an assault on Koeglin Lighthouse. I should bring these to Koeglin Village.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Shell-Tide Village is under duress from the presence of the Worm Cult. In return for aiding in a ceremony to cleanse the tides, the village's tide-reader has promised to send warriors to aid the Stirk Fellowship.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Jee-Lar needs bug repellent candles for Cyrodilic Collections' explorers in Murkmire. He requested that I gather materials so his contact, Tamira Dobar, can create these candles.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Count Verandis Ravenwatch tracked Lady Belain and Rada al-Saran to a mysterious Dwarven edifice. But with the keystone in hand, our enemies have a clear advantage. Braving this ruin and learning its secrets may be our best hope of stopping them.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Tamien, an ex-Red Rook bandit, claims he wants to save the town of Eagle's Brook. The Lion Guard, however, don't trust him. Tamien says the Bloodthorns are turning townfolk into zombies. He wants my help to prepare a spell to protect the villagers.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A tribe of Argonians is at odds with a group of Imperial soldiers. The Argonians say their people are missing, and they blame the Imperials. Heem-Jas asked me to act as a mediator to figure out what's going on.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Wayward Guardians fear that Gray Host forces still lurk in the halls of Nchuand-Zel beneath Markarth. They need them driven from those halls.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Green-Venom-Tongue learned a few things from the Black Dragon's journal that seem to point to his former Sanctuary. He wants to go back there and try to confirm the Black Dragon's claims.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met an Argonian named Malosza who told me of a brutal tribe named the Sul-Xan who invaded his home. He requested I travel to Rockgrove if I wish to lend aid.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Reeh-La's Mining Samples",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found Reeh-La, an Argonian prospector, dead in an out-of-the-way corner of Blackreach.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Survivors of the plague from Narsis have built a refugee camp inside long-abandoned crypts. <<1>> and her husband came to join the group, but became separated.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Mane, on his way to the Handfasting in Silvenar, suddenly attacked his entourage and fled. Lord Gharesh-ri, the Speaker of the Mane, asked me to find him.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The hunt-wife of the Seamount clan thinks the chief's daughter is not mindful of her duties to the clan. She believes I could help sort things out.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Skald-King dispatched a party of sword-thanes to investigate unnatural storms swirling around Icereach. Alas, a coven of witches killed most of the warriors. I must venture into the aged keep, kill the witches within, and search for survivors.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A moon-sugar plantation suffered a terrible fire. The family in charge of the plantation needs a hand to recover from their tragedy.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A villager from Tava's Blessing asked that I seek out a Thronekeeper named Luala al-Tava.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I'm working with Razum-dar, at the town of Mathiisen. He's looking into reports of the Veiled Heritance in the area for Queen Ayrenn.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Igeke Rat-Bite no longer trusts her companions after the mysterious death of their cousin, Vareda. She's requested that I collect a nearby treasure chest, which can only be opened by her family's blood.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Well-Armed Savages",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Ink-Parched",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Star-Gazer Sariyaah asked me to look for Trapper Marcien to find out why they never returned.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts, which requests the indiscriminate slaughter of citizens of the Gold Coast.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Bastion Nymic - Fallen Hues",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Lady Belain seeks a mysterious Dwarven relic called the Arkthzand Keystone for her ally, Rada al-Saran. Count Verandis wants me to find the keystone before it winds up in the hands of the Gray Host.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A Senche-raht necromancer named Thannar the Graveprowler stalks the ruins southwest of Rimmen, urging the corpses buried there to rise from their graves. Left unchecked, his ranks of undead followers could swell.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "An Ill-Fated Venture",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a letter on a dead man named Tavo in the Lost City of the Na-Totambu. His wife, Nahrina, wanted him to recover some Yokudan relics  and return to Sentinel to pay off a debt. I can recover the relics in his stead.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts, which requests the indiscriminate slaughter of citizens of Stormhaven.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The guardian star sign of the Warrior has failed to appear to protect the mortal world from the Serpent. One of the Star-Gazers needs help uncovering what might be happening.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Pledge: White-Gold Tower",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>> has challenged me to explore the White-Gold Tower in the Imperial City.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Ember opened up a bit about her past. Apparently, she was part of a tight-knit group of street kids for much of her younger life until her makeshift family mysteriously vanished from Skywatch. She's determined to find them and asked for my help.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Arch-Mage Valeyn believes I'm here to help protect the Academy against some unnamed threat. While he determines what this threat is, he asked me to help him with another matter.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Jorunn the Skald-King requested I meet with his agent to look into a plot that threatens not only Skyrim, but potentially all of Tamriel.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I've reached the siege range. Adalmor advised me to try each weapon. I should also talk to Looks-Forward and Lirtis to learn more about the weapons.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I have been welcomed into the bizarre realm of the Daedric Demiprince Fa-Nuit-Hen. In order to test my mettle and demonstrate my skills, I've agreed to enter the Maelstrom Arena, where deadly challenges created by Fa-Nuit-Hen's Barons await me.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Kidnappers abducted Skordo the Knife, but their caravan fell prey to a Dragon attack. The abductors left the hard-nosed Orc behind, but dragged off two of his companions. Skordo wants to free his friends and put a stop to the kidnappers' schemes.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Divine Prosecution seeks able-bodied adventurers to assist with the enforcement of laws by performing contract work throughout Summerset.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A ragged preacher warned me that my wealth and status attract a lot of dangerous attention in Elsweyr, particularly from the folk-hero-turned-god, Rajhin. The preacher solicited me to steal offerings to appease the Khajiit thief-god.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Something is definitely happening at Fort Amol. Groups of high-ranking Nords, Argonians, and Dark Elves are on hand, and the guards are turning travelers away from the inn. I should try to figure out what's going on.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Kassandra, having evaded Jaxsik-Orrn and Xukas, entered a second xanmeer called Vakka-Bok. Famia and I must enter this vast ruin and prevent Kassandra from acquiring the Remnant of Argon.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Eveli Sharp-Arrow and Lyranth the Dremora are chasing the same mystery-a secret concerning the last Longhouse Emperor, Leovic. Clues point to his steward Farrul Lupus, who hired Eveli to acquire a strange book. We need to bring it to him in Riften.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "King Dynar has devised a two-pronged attack to take control of the Reaver Citadel. It utilizes the old Fighters and Mages Guilds' halls located in this ancient Nirn city.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Darien discovered that we need three shard-keys to open the three locks that protect Angof's inner sanctum.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Torinaan's strange little relic-keeper worries the holy relics will be corrupted by Daedric energies.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maj al-Ragath of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore the cavern called Spindleclutch beneath Glenumbra.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Urgarlag Chief-bane of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore Oathsworn Pit.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "JB - Generic Wave Event - Surv",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Bolu of the Dead-Water tribe, which calls itself the Naga-Kur, wants me to go to Bok-Xul and accomplish the task he set before me.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "We recovered the Dragonhorn, but we have no idea what to do with it. While Abnur Tharn attempts to learn more, Khamira wants me to stop Zumog Phoom from reassembling Cadwell's original body-the evil Cadwell the Betrayer.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A savage band of Sul-Xan Argonians raided the ancient city of Rockgrove. Led by Flame-Herald Bahsei, they plan to summon something named Xalvakka. I must purge the area of these brutes and stop their plan before this creature enters our realm.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Drublog Orcs attacked the village of Tanglehaven. <<1>> said the survivors barely managed to fend them off. After the massacre, the surviving Tanglehaven militia chased the Drublog into the forest-including <<2>>, <<1>>'s daughter.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Lady Clarisse Laurent and her man-servant Stibbons, along with a number of research assistants on loan from the Mages Guild, have been studying the ruins of Bal Fell. Now, everyone but Lady Laurent has disappeared.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Glirion the Redbeard of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore Tempest Island, a storm-tossed outcropping off the coast of Malabal Tor.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Glirion the Redbeard of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore Selene's Web, a spider-haunted grove in Reaper's March.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Even though they're dead, Ix-Utha's Argonian brethren still act as slaves to the risen Chimer. They've returned to serve their cruel spectral masters.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Naj-Caldeesh is an abandoned xanmeer with a legendary secret. Talen-Lah and his band of Wuj-Laxul necromancers overran the xanmeer as soon as it was discovered. Talen-lah wants to take the xanmeer's power for himself.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>> continues to restore the long-lost reputation of Orc cuisine. She needs additional rare ingredients for a special dessert.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The various threats to the Systres Archipelago have been dealt with and now Lady Arabelle wants to get on with the long-delayed peace talks. First, however, she has a few other tasks for me to take care of.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Blind Path, led by the Blind, invaded a subsection of Maelstrom called Bedlam Veil. Fa-Nuit-Hen asked me to figure out what the Blind is looking for and deal with the Blind Path army.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Leel-Vata asked me to rescue the captured Argonian villagers from the Khajiiti pirates.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Covenant has seized Fort Virak. They're serving under the command of General Serien. The Pact's army-led by the Indorils, <<1>>, and Walks-in-Ash-has besieged the fort in an attempt to retake it.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maj al-Ragath of the Undaunted has challenged me to delve the Banished Cells beneath Auridon.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met a strange Imperial who was being held captive by the Daggerfall Covenant. He believes he knows how to defeat the cursed army of Anka-Ra that has laid siege to Craglorn since the Celestials appeared.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maj al-Ragath of the Undaunted has challenged me to brave Fungal Grotto in the caverns beneath Stonefalls.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Cold-Blooded Vengeance",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "After learning that Mulaamnir the Dragon considers Euraxia, the usurper queen of Rimmen, to be nothing more than a puppet, Abnur Tharn believes parley is our best course of action-especially considering the current state of the Khajiiti army.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Clan Mother Shuzura has apparently been very hard on her assistants. There are problems in the little town of S'ren-ja. Perhaps I can help out.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Blue Sash Guild, a group of tight knit adventurers, is on the verge of breaking up. Kuzam-jo asked me to help put an end to their infighting before it is too late.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "King Razor-Tusk Hunt",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Huntmaster Sorim-Nakar of the Erabenimsun Ashlander tribe has given me a challenge. He wants me to hunt the powerful kagouti called King Razor-Tusk.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maj al-Ragath of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore the ancient complex beneath Elden Root, the Elden Hollow, in the center of Grahtwood.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I received a voucher for a special-occasion cake from the renowned master baker, Chef Donolon.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maj al-Ragath has challenged me to explore the kwama mines of Darkshade Caverns beneath Deshaan.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>> suspects the Dominion skin-stealers are based out of <<2>>.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Count Carolus still owes us what he promised for taking on his contract-information concerning the Black Dragon. Astara wants to find out what the Count knows.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met Sahmazim outside a ruin called Xul-Katama, an ancient monastery of the death-dancers. With the Worm Cult encroaching on the monastery, he hired me to rescue some stone tablets before the cultists discover them.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>> has nearly restored the long-lost reputation of Orc cuisine. She needs a few more rare ingredients to complete her masterpiece.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Raynor and Kireth Vanos, self-proclaimed Dwemer experts, left Morrowind to look for long lost knowledge and lore within Skyrim's Dwarven ruins.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Queen Ayrenn ordered the once-forbidden island of Summerset to open its borders and welcome outsiders to its expansive shores. Razum-dar, an agent of the Queen, has come to the island to make sure the decree is followed to the letter.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maj al-Ragath of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore the Fungal Grotto beneath Stonefalls.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Hooke, an ex-thief, believes someone is murdering members of his old gang, the Scarlets. He asked me to help him find the remaining Scarlets and protect them from the killer.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a note from a trapper near a snared wormmouth called Versidue. The note says if I return Versidue to Star-Gazer Sariyaah in Ontus, I'll be rewarded.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Urgarlag Chief-bane of the Undaunted has challenged me to free Lep Seclusa from Orpheon the Tactician's army.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Teeba-Ja was a member of the Bitterhand Bandits, but when they became more violent, she decided to leave. She wants to start a new life in Shornhelm.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Peek-Ereel gave me a message from Governor Keshu's spymaster, Tee-Wan. Tee-Wan needs my help with a private and urgent matter.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maj al-Ragath of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore the complex of sewers beneath Wayrest, dead center in the region called Stormhaven.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Bolu of the Dead-Water tribe, called the Naga-Kur in the Argonian tongue, wants me to go to the Echoing Hollow and accomplish the task he set before me.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met an injured hunter out in Eastern Solstice who asked me to help finish hunting a pack of bear-lizards. Apparently, they attacked and killed his friend, Golvyni. I agreed to help lure them to his friend's trap.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "While in the Goblin camp, I found a Nord corpse clutching a runestone that bears the name \"Hodmar Iron-Kettle.\"",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>> asked me to deliver orders to a rebel spy in Imperial-held Cheydinhal.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Deep Tombs of Xul-Haj",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I learned that the Worm Cult is planning to raid a Stone-Nest necropolis to raise an army of undead. And Vanus Galerion may be imprisoned there as well. I need to stop the cult and rescue Vanus.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Tree-Minder's Fate",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Mystery surrounds Forsaken Hamlet. An Argonian tree-minder lies murdered at the edge of her village.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Cold-Blooded Revenge",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Urgarlag Chief-bane of the Undaunted has challenged me to remove Valinna from her position as the leader of the Scribes of Mora in Scrivener's Hall.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The time to confront Vox has arrived-but it seems that to defeat her, I need to die by her hammer. The Blessing of Veloth should protect me, but can I return from the dead?",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Shadowfen's Vicecanon Hrondar sent Saervild Steel-Wind to Bogmother's ruins to collect Argonian relics.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Sees-All-Colors has had Doshia's journal translated. From it she believes she may have discovered information relating to the mysterious Mortuum Vivicus.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Verandis detected a growing concentration of dark energy-Void energy-within Nighthollow Keep. Perhaps we'll find the Dark Heart somewhere within those ancient ruins.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I've accomplished great deeds with Tanval Indoril, <<1>>, and Walks-in-Ash. We've returned Tanval's Vanguard to the Ebonheart Pact, and convinced the spirits of Tormented Spire to open Sadal's prison.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Three-Pronged Approach",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "This is the Talking Quest.  The purpose of this quest is to talk to people and things, to  make sure the conversation system is still working.  Tally-ho!",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Guildmaster Sees-All-Colors has plans to make use of the crystal and tome we found in the depths of Mzeneldt.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Arch-Mage Valeyn thinks his visions are somehow connected to the evil Magistrix Vox. Unfortunately, before he could learn more, something blocked his magic.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I received a voucher for a special-occasion cake from the renowned master baker, Chef Donolon.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A high-ranking member of the Mages Guild, <<1>> wants me to perform a task for her.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Time-Lost Warrior",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Rites of the Sul-Xan",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Sul-Xan Argonians are a tribe of vicious cultists who kidnap people around Blackwood for human sacrifice. I agreed to rescue captives held by the Sul-Xan and eliminate the cultists.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met a Redguard named Paldeen, held prisoner by the Khajiit bandits in the Lost City of the Na-Totambu. He asked for my help in opening the sealed inner chamber.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Magister Vox stole an item of power from the Tribunal Temple-the hammer known as Veloth's Judgment. She fled east, away from Mournhold. Almalexia asked me to track her down before she gains the full power of the artifact.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts, which requests the indiscriminate slaughter of citizens of East March.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>> continues to restore the long-lost reputation of Orc cuisine. She hired me to collect additional rare ingredients throughout Wrothgar.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a note on a dead bandit. Their leader, a man named Oath-Breaker, has orders to capture villagers, so he can trade them for supplies.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Outside the school of blades called Rahni'Za, I encountered an initiate of the school who told me that the Sword-Disciples have been turned into thralls by a traitor. This betrayer now hides in the cavern at the end of the school's five trials.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met Ibrula, a friend of the Star-Gazers who is trying to get into a ruined temple called the Seeker's Archive. She hopes to discover information inside that will help defeat the Celestials.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Stormfist soldiers ransacked Voljar's Meadery and slaughtered the family-all because they wanted free mead. Haraldar's wife was one of the Voljars killed in the attack. He wants to reopen the meadery, and he recruited his four brothers to help.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I returned to Dhalmora. All of the Bleakrock villagers are gone. Aera informed me of a large Covenant attack on Bal Foyen. Darj has lead some of the non-combatants to Fort Zeren. Captain Rana is leading a defense of the docks.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a notice seeking brave and able-bodied adventurers for work.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I arrived in Eastmarch, in the Nord city of Windhelm. The place bustles with revelers as a celebration honoring the Skald-King is underway.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Thane Mera, enraged by the death of the racer Hadring, demands that the assassins pay for this crime. She wants me, Windhelm's Champion, to deal with this-personally.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "An Argonian named Bishalus is afraid that nix-hounds have devoured her friend, Gena. She claimed to have made a flute that could tame the beasts, but she has yet to return.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "According to <<1>>, a group of Naga extremists in Xi-Tsei called Sul-Xan are capturing and sacrificing innocent people. His client wants me to infiltrate the temple and destroy the extremists' ritual tools, then return for my reward.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Skald-King and the other Ebonheart Pact leaders have established a base at Jorunn's Stand. While the Skald-King recovers, the leaders need to decide how to deal with Fildgor Orcthane.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The sentry captain, Ula-Reen, keeps the camp secure. She asked me to help.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Aspera Giant-Friend says the giants are about to go to war against the Stormfists that hold Cradlecrush because their mammoths were stolen. As long as I oppose the Stormfists, these giants will consider me to be an ally.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I wandered into Cragwallow, a small settlement used by the Skald-King's royal work crews. After a lot of hard work maintaining the roads, they're preparing to throw a party.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Lothgar Steady-Hand was grievously wounded by the creatures that attacked Cragwallow. He appears to be dying.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Gwendis of House Ravenwatch recruited me to help free captives trapped inside Greymoor Keep by Lady Essenia, a cruel vampiric sovereign. Gwendis's friend, Adusa-daro, is among those prisoners.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Jorunn the Skald-King has been poisoned. Now he lies in an eternal slumber. The Ternion monks, who revere the Three Old Gods, attempt to cure him. But time is running out.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maormer Sea Vipers invaded Ilayas Ruins, searching for a weather-controlling relic called the Sphere of Storms. I've been asked to help the stormwardens defend the sphere until reinforcements arrive.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Lord Vivec's condition continues to deteriorate as his energy drains away. Archcanon Tarvus believes that Chodala's staff holds the key to saving the Warrior-Poet. However, it also makes the Ashlander practically impervious to harm.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "After events in Shadowfen, Vicecanon Heita-Meen and I must travel to Eastmarch, in Skyrim.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I've arrived in Nimalten to find the city under threat. Thane Fjora was attacked by her housecarl. Aera Earth-Turner, my old friend from Bleakrock Isle, is leading an investigation.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Preparations were completed just in time - the undead are attacking Fullhelm Fort! <<1>> has asked me to help defeat the attack.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Lieutenant Koruni asked me to deliver a dispatch detailing Fort Morvunskar's status to Thane Oda Wolf-Sister at Fort Amol.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "A Fine-Feathered Foe",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I have accepted a contract to defeat the creature Wraith-of-Crows and other Daedric incursions in Clockwork City's Radius.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Numani-Rasi of the Urshilaku Ashlander tribe has requested that I explore the ruins of the Daedric shrine Ebernanit and gather as many historic relics as I can find.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Argonian Steady-Hand believes he's the best hunter in Eastmarch, better than any Nord or Dark Elf alive. He's challenged me to a hunting contest. If I can shoot a number of rabbits in one minute, or catch the rabbit called Golden Jack, I win.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Reach clans Six-Fords and Eagleseers don't get along. They plan to rectify that through the marriage of two of their young members, Eslyn and Madearn. A handfasting rite must be performed to announce their intention to marry.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I received a voucher for a special-occasion cake from the renowned master baker, Chef Donolon.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The garrison at Cey-Tarn Keep has been terrorized by a spate of unusual disappearances and deaths. A monster hunter named Silurie has enlisted my help to stop the killings.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The warrior Daljari Half-Troll oversees the Trial of the Body, a test of brawn over brain.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a notice about the opportunity to join a guild of like-minded adventurers.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A Khajiiti merchant calling himself <<1>> claims to have found a way inside Belarata, a long-sealed Ayleid ruin.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I discovered the Library of Dusk, an Ayleid ruin, just beyond the Hollow City. Several treasure-hunters and scholars in the service of the Mages Guild have been trapped within the ruins by Daedra.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts, which requests the indiscriminate slaughter of citizens of Stonefalls.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Mages Guild hired dungeon-delvers and scholars to bolster their expedition force. A group of these treasure hunters are trapped in the Library of Dusk, including Kireth Vanos' brother, Raynor.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Captain One-Eye was forced to kill her own crew, and now she's vowed to destroy the apparition that controlled the cursed sailors.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I have purged the Veiled Heritance from Mathiisen. Now I should meet up with Razum-dar in Skywatch to learn what other plans the Veiled Heritance has.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Bolu of the Dead-Water tribe, called the Naga-Kur in the Argonian tongue, wants me to go to the Echoing Hollow and accomplish the task he set before me.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Cyrodilic Collections' operation in Murkmire is growing, and more explorers mean more mouths to feed. With my help, Jee-Lar plans to send cured meats to Black Marsh.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>>'s pet-a Dwarven construct-has broken down. She wants me to steal parts so that she can repair it.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maj al-Ragath wants to introduce me to the Undaunted pledge.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "In the confusion of battle, Sylvian Herius left a family heirloom in the Imperial-held cathedral across the river.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The healers of Root-Whisper Village are in need of a rare aloe that grows in Vakka-Bok. I'll need to make my way past the dangerous creatures that lurk there in order to gather this plant.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The hunters and warriors of the Root-Whisper tribe are in desperate need for hackwing hides in order to craft leather armor. I've agreed to hunt down these beasts.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I used the key to search the House Dres farmhouses outside Mournhold. I found a suspicious-looking trap door hidden under a rug. Naryu thinks we'll discover a connection to the Maulborn down there.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Mane has released Dro-m'athra spirits on Fort Grimwatch! Twins <<1>> and <<2>>, Khajiit Champions, lead the fight against the creatures.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "After eating too many moon-sugar candies, <<1>>'s Khajiit husband, <<2>>, ran screaming into the forest.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts, which requests the indiscriminate slaughter of citizens of Grahtwood.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I helped the people of S'ren-ja with their many and varied problems.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "In the wake of a Dro-m'Athra attack, a lunar priest has asked me to save a priceless relic from the vault behind Moonmont.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts, which requests the indiscriminate slaughter of citizens of Bangkorai.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts, which requests the indiscriminate slaughter of citizens of Malabal Tor.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Bolu of the Dead-Water tribe, which calls itself the Naga-Kur, wants me to go to Bok-Xul and accomplish the task he set before me.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Ufgra gra-Gum says that undead creatures infest the ruins of Culotte to the southwest of Cropsford.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Anti-Venom Agitation",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Jee-Lar informed me that a Wood Elf named Mindileth knows the recipe for a particularly potent anti-venom. This brew may prove vital for the company's explorers in Murkmire. Apparently, the ingredients-and Mindileth-can be found in Grahtwood.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Though I've gathered all the tablets, the Xinchei-Konu remains powerless. Jekka-Wass Vozei wishes to perform a ritual to help the monument regain its magical properties, but needs the help of his mentor Nisswo Paraxeeh to do so.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The farmers of Root-Whisper Village are in need of a rare mushroom that grows in Blight Bog Sump. I'll need to make my way past the dangerous creatures that lurk there in order to gather this plant.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A woman claiming to be the leader of the Scaled Court requested my help. This Regent Cassipia wants me to help her stop the Scaled Court's process for creating a new type of creature for the Serpent's growing army-the mantikora.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "After the death of Prince Naemon, Vicereeve Pelidil assumed leadership of the Veiled Heritance and stole the Staff of Magnus. Razum-dar has tracked him to somewhere in the area of Woodhearth.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Skin-Stealer's Lair",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>> was replaced by a Dominion skin-stealer. I need to find the imposter and stop the remaining skin-stealers in <<2>>.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Maormer seek to prevent the Dominion from establishing themselves on <<1>>. They've launched a full-scale attack on <<2>>.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Soul-Meld Mage",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met Gadris the Dark Elf and Zur the Khajiit. These two mages share a single body, as their souls were melded at this Vile Laboratory when they arrived in Coldharbour. This soul-meld has weakened them. If they remain combined, they will surely die.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "A Death-Dancer's Duty",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Death-Dancer Teerad of the Tide-Born Argonians needs someone to locate the missing tidal votives of the three warriors who recently were killed, so he can perform a funerary ritual. I agreed to help him.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>>, the hearth-wife to <<2>>, believes he was murdered. She suspects <<3>>, <<2>>'s hunt-wife, conspired to kill him. <<1>> is convinced <<3>> secretly worships Boethiah, the Daedric Prince of Treachery.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Suraj, a member of Captain One-Eye's crew, begged for my help in stopping Velehk Sain, a pirate captain pursuing their ship out of Coldharbour.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>>, the slave dealer who runs <<2>>, sent his thugs to kill me and failed. His business partner, <<3>>, has grown tired of his slave-trading operation and wants me to eliminate him.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Moon-Sugar Medicament",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The chief of the Ash'abah and many of the tribe's warriors have been poisoned, most likely by the Withered Hand. I agreed to help Talia at-Marimah gather ingredients for an antidote.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The army has been gathered and the time has come to take the battle to Molag Bal! But to reach the planar vortex at the heart of the Dark Lord's inner sanctum, we have to cross the well-defended Chasm.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Lunar Priestess Kauzanabi-jo has indicated I should make for the temple of Moonmont. The Champions, the new candidates for the Mane, will join me there.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The priestess Kauzanabi-jo told me my next goal should be to help the people of Arenthia. Apparently Mane Akkhuz-ri is somewhere amid the Colovian invaders of the city.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met Oorbesh, a ghost-hunting Orc, outside the very haunted Corelanya Manor. She agreed to cut me in for a share of treasure that's supposed to be hidden inside the manor if I help her find it before a rival ghost hunter beats her to it.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A group of vile mercenaries called the Painted Eye invaded Kemel-Ze to loot Sotha Sil's experiments. Thoryn Armas, a priest of the Tribunal Temple asked for my help to rid Kemel-Ze of the ransacking mercenaries.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I have been welcomed into the bizarre realm of the Daedric Demiprince Fa-Nuit-Hen. In order to test my mettle and demonstrate my skills, I've agreed to enter the Maelstrom Arena, where deadly challenges created by Fa-Nuit-Hen's Barons await me.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The priestess Kauzanabi-jo told me my next goal should be to make for the temple in Rawl'kha. I need to aid the Lunar Champions in their journey.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I ran into a very hung-over mage in Rawl'kha. He had too much to drink, lost several magical relics, and now fears he'll never gain an apprenticeship to Telenger the Artificer.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Dimik-ei, the sister from Sharp's forgotten past, wishes to meet with him again. Sharp thinks she might be able to help us track down his former oppressor, Sondivel the Reformer.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I learned that Vro-Kuul-Sha the Deepreaver recently defeated a group of Buoyant Armigers who were attempting to follow in Lord Vivec's footsteps.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The eccentric artificer and dungeon-delver, Raynor Vanos, needs more data for his experiments. He's certain that the information he requires can be found in a Dwarven ruin called Zthenganaz.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met a Khajiit called Cold-Eyes who is looking to collect a debt. He'll give me a cut if I help him.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Zerith received a suspicious summons from High Cantor Viti to meet in Pa'alat. Perhaps she finally realized we share an enemy in the Rajaska, but Zerith-var suspects it may be a trap.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a journal that belonged to a monk of the Lunar faith named Yenadar. The journal mentions that he has a sister named Kala in S'ren-ja. I should return the journal to her.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Bastion Nymic - Writhing Wastes",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "After defeating the Maormer assault on Khenarthi's Roost, Razum-dar has asked me to report to <<1>> in the Auridon city of Vulkhel Guard.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Lady Clarisse Laurent is on the trail of the Emerald Chalice, a relic stolen from the Mages Guild by the exiled Nord mage, Malofar. She tracked him here to Breagha-Fin.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "According to Jee-Lar, poison-sniffing skinks can provide some much-needed security in the wilds of Murkmire. He needs me to acquire one of these valuable lizards in Alik'r.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The ruins of the ancient Wood Elf village of Gil-Var-Delle is under the corrupting influence of Molag Bal. The Worm Cult is active here, and my help is needed to put an end to their schemes.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The riddles I uncovered with Xukas and Jaxsik-Orrn pointed us to a mysterious locale known as the Swallowed Grove. According to Famia, I will have to undertake a dream-wallow vision to learn the truth of the Remnant of Argon.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>>, delegate-at-large for the Ebonheart Pact Cultural Exchange, misplaced his scepter of office after a night of wild festivities. He asked me to help him find it.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Legionary-turned-constable Yabren deputized me to help her investigate a series of suspicious deaths in the town of Ontus, including the death of her father Ulbren, the previous town constable.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Death-Hunts",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a notice calling for warriors to join a Death-Hunt.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maj al-Ragath has challenged me to explore the ruins beneath Grahtwood, the Veteran Elden Hollow.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Pledge: Naj-Caldeesh",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Urgarlag Chief-bane of the Undaunted challenged me to explore Naj-Caldeesh and get rid of the necromancers inside.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a journal on the body of Klaandor Axe-Bearer. It details his transformation into a vampire. Seems like he was looking for someone to kill him.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a journal that belonged to a monk of the lunar faith named Yenadar. The journal mentions that he has a sister named <<1>> in S'ren-ja. I should return the journal to her.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Imperial Magus-General Septima Tharn captured King Emeric and took him into the Chamber of Passage. It's apparently a gateway to the plane known as the Far Shores, where Redguards go in the afterlife.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Dark Elf Ashur has come to Hakoshae to investigate Magnate Feina-Darak. Rumor has it that she's the descendant of the Akaviri Potentate. I agreed to help him in his investigation.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A Daedra has taken over Nilata Ruins. Having possessed a farmer's wife, the Daedra is luring travelers into her lair-likely to their doom.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Urgarlag Chief-bane of the Undaunted has challenged me to rid Earthen Root Enclave of the Firesong invaders.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Arch-Mage's Boon",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "We found a way to sneak into the sealed city of Northpoint-a tunnel used by smugglers and black marketeers. Now we need to head inside and find a way to free the city from Lleraya Montclair's grasp.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met a priest of Y'ffre who seeks to heal the scarred ruin of Gil-Var-Delle by mixing blessed water into the falls that feed into the river of the vale. She asked me to help her in her task.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Cadwell has turned the Harborage into his new home-for the time being, at any rate.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A Pact soldier and his brother were captured by bandits after being caught spying. They were investigating the cult-like activity of the bandits.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met a courier named Wuleen-Kur who asked me to help him make an urgent delivery to a hermit named Hecicla.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "We put an end to Reezal-Jul and Lleraya. Now we need to deal with Baron Montclair. But to reach Montclair in his citadel atop the Doomcrag, we first need to find a way through the Shrouded Pass.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Star-Gazers",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Captain Ronag at Shinji's Scarp asked me to deliver a dispatch to Clan Murtag soldiers near the at-Tura estate.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a grave-stake lying next to a note indicating that it was stolen. I should find out who to return the grave-stake to.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met Ibrula, a friend of the Star-Gazers who is trying to get into a ruined temple called the Seeker's Archive. She hopes to discover information inside that will help defeat the Celestials.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Urgarlag Chief-bane of the Undaunted challenged me to explore Black Gem Foundry in Coldharbour and put a stop to production there.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Outside the school of blades called Rahni'Za, I encountered an intiate of the school who told me that the Sword-Disciples have been turned into thralls by a traitor. This betrayer now hides in the cavern at the end of the school's five trials.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Khajiiti temple of Two Moons at Tenmar has been afflicted by mass hysteria. The priests blindly follow the bizarre prophecies of their Moon-Bishop, which grow more deranged and deluded by the day.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The priestess Kauzanabi-jo told me my next goal should be to help the Lunar Champions Rid-Thar spoke of. I should seek them out at the fort known as Grimwatch.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A young Khajiiti mage named Narama-ko sought my help outside the Abode of Ignominy. Apparently, the notes and memory stones of a powerful mage lie within this crumbling, subterranean temple. She assures me she could put them to good use.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a letter from High-King Emeric offering amnesty to the bandits who reside in the ruins of Watcher's Hold. The <<z:1>> also brought a chest of gold as a sign of the king's good faith.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "We ended the Dreadsails siege on Vastyr, but at the cost of a great many lives-including Count Mornard and Archdruids Rahval and Ellic. And the Firesong now have all three sacred seeds. We need to find a way to stop Archdruid Orlaith.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>> attempted to enter an Oblivion Gate with a group of Undaunted to save his wife, <<2>>. He failed. I'm to help him get her back-if she still lives.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I encountered a Star-Gazer who told me that two High Elf women inside the Crossroad Tavern claim to be aspects of the Celestial Mage. I should talk to them and investigate their claims.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Safa al-Satakalaam, a priest of Satakal, is at odds with the Scaled Court. Three of her most powerful acolytes have deserted her to worship the Celestial Serpent. She wants me to punish these traitors and deny their power to the Scaled Court.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A woman claiming to be the leader of the Scaled Court requested my help. This Regent Cassipia wants me to help her stop the Scaled Court's process for creating a new type of creature for the Serpent's growing army-the mantikora.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maj al-Ragath of the Undaunted has challenged me to delve the Banished Cells beneath Auridon.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Time-Lost Warrior",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maj al-Ragath of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore the cavern called Spindleclutch beneath Glenumbra.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maj al-Ragath of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore the kwama mine called Darkshade Caverns, which lies beneath Deshaan.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Maj al-Ragath of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore the tunnels and caverns that lie beneath Wayrest, the Veteran Wayrest Sewers.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Sharp says we finally have a way forward to find the kidnapped Dimik-ei and stop Sondivel Ulres the Reformer once and for all.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a book describing an ancient Nedic hero named Ranev the Coal-Eyed Wanderer and her legendary pilgrimage along \"The Gray Passage.\" According to the text, those who complete the pilgrimage in the allotted time gain the favor of the Stars.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Daedra have occupied the White-Gold Tower, and I have agreed to help Moth Priest Terran Arminus retrieve an Elder Scroll left inside the Tower Library.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Khajiit's ancient enemy, the dro-m'Athra, have emerged from the Dark Behind the World and claimed the Temple of Seven Riddles for the Ghost Moon, Lorkhaj.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Deetum-Jas asked me to take notes on things I observe inside a Daedric ruin for a local poet who is looking for inspiration.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>> wants to restore the long-lost reputation of Orc cuisine, but her assistant is missing. I agreed to help her until he arrives.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "King Kurog seems to be in a foul mood, which has affected everyone in the royal court. His shield-wife indicates that tensions at the keep are on the verge of boiling over. I wonder what happened to darken the king's usually boisterous spirits?",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The minions of Molag Bal are rounding up the Imperial City's clergy and mercilessly torturing them. The Drake of Blades has asked for my help in rescuing one of these prisoners-a priest named Egnatius.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A concerned clerk named <<1>> believes there is a grave threat to the well-being of future generations if the Imperial recordkeeping falls to war.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Walks-Softly needs help dealing with a personal and delicate situation that involves an old friend from his past.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Vampire hunter Mel Adrys has come to Hrota Cave to track down the dangerous vampire lord Zalar-do, who has been preying on the people of Anvil. I promised to help him slay the vampire and rescue the victims she kidnapped.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Razum-dar tracked an Imperial war criminal to the Garlas Agea ruins to make her pay for attacking innocent noncombatants in Bravil. I agreed to help him dispatch this Captain Jena Apinia and recover the items they stole.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Mani-Kai, a Bright-Throat Argonian aiding the Stirk Fellowship, wishes to speak with the leader of Xor-Hist, but the village is under threat of a Worm Cult attack. She needs my help to light the village's signal pyres.",
