esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Black Hand has decreed that Lyra the Black Dragon must die for her crimes against the Brotherhood. Green-Venom-Tongue has gone to Knightsgrave to perform the task. Astara has asked me to back him up.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Speaker Terenus wants to cut off the head of the group that has been moving against the Dark Brotherhood-he wants us to kill Artorius, the Primate of Akatosh. He wants the death to happen quickly, before the Order of the Hour attacks the Sanctuary.",
