esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts, which requests the indiscriminate slaughter of citizens of the Rift.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The guardian star sign of the Warrior has failed to appear to protect the mortal world from the Serpent. One of the Star-Gazers needs help uncovering what might be happening.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Star-Gazers",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met a strange Imperial who was being held captive by the Daggerfall Covenant. He believes he knows how to defeat the cursed army of Anka-Ra that has laid siege to Craglorn since the Celestials appeared.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I encountered a Star-Gazer who told me that two High Elf women inside the Crossroad Tavern claim to be aspects of the Celestial Mage. I should talk to them and investigate their claims.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Captain Telomure has asked me to destroy a pearl that's been stolen by a member of the Divine Prosecution, Justiciar Avanaire. The pearl is somewhere in Tor-Hame-Khard.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a book describing an ancient Nedic hero named Ranev the Coal-Eyed Wanderer and her legendary pilgrimage along \"The Gray Passage.\" According to the text, those who complete the pilgrimage in the allotted time gain the favor of the Stars.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Two Argonian slaves named Eoki and Sun-in-Shadow have hatched a plot to win their freedom from the Dark Elves of House Telvanni.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Toad-Tongue Goblin tribe took over an old ruin. And they ate a scholar who ventured in to study them. I agreed to confront War Chief Zathmoz and recover any notes I can find.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A Dark Elf businessman named Malur Rethan is convinced that his brother and partner, Benar, is hiding something in the Vassir-Didanat ebony mine. He asked me to investigate.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Trial of Five-Clawed Guile",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The recently freed Argonian slave, Sun-in-Shadow, seeks to continue her climb through the ranks of House Telvanni. She needs my help to claim the next title.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I've been hired to defeat a nix-ox that has been eating mushrooms the wizard Bravosi Felder is attempting to research. I'm also required to collect samples of the mushrooms while in the area.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Jee-Lar asked me to help recruit adventurers to join Cyrodilic Collections' expedition to Murkmire. Posting recruitment handbills and performing a traditional Argonian dance will help drum up interest.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "With my help, Sun-in-Shadow achieved the rank of retainer in the Great House Telvanni. If she is to help free Eoki, she will need to climb the ranks even further. Unfortunately, becoming an oathman may present a greater challenge than she expects.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Huntmaster Sorim-Nakar of the Erabenimsun Ashlander tribe has given me a challenge. He wants me to hunt the deadly nix-ox called Great Zexxin.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Tarra-Suj Hunt",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Huntmaster Sorim-Nakar of the Erabenimsun Ashlander tribe has given me a challenge. He wants me to hunt the deadly nix-hound called Tarra-Suj.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Mother Jagged-Claw Hunt",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Huntmaster Sorim-Nakar of the Erabenimsun Ashlander tribe has given me a challenge. He wants me to hunt the giant mudcrab called Mother Jagged-Claw.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Ash-Eater Hunt",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Huntmaster Sorim-Nakar of the Erabenimsun Ashlander tribe has given me a challenge. He wants me to hunt the dire ash beetle called Ash-Eater.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Several ancient stone tablets were unearthed at a site northeast of Xul-Katama in eastern Solstice. However, a dangerous Voidmother named Soulcaller reportedly now haunts the area. I need to defeat Soulcaller and retrieve the tablets.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "My ambitious companion, Sun-in-Shadow, succeeded in replacing Magister Gothren's Mouth, Ralasa Delvi. But even success carries risk in Sadrith Mora. Rumor has it that Magister Gothren leaves no slight unpunished.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Adusa-daro needs my help to rescue her friend Kathad from a clan of evil vampires known as the Lothid, and their leader, Boss Trenlor.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "After a harrowing experience at the hands of Magister Gothren, Sun-in-Shadow finds herself at a crossroads-torn between a mage's ambition and the fruits of companionship. Dedicating herself to one may well destroy her chances at the other.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Numani-Rasi of the Urshilaku Ashlander tribe has requested that I explore the ruins of the Daedric shrine Assarnatamat and gather as many historic relics as I can find.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Numani-Rasi of the Urshilaku Ashlander tribe has requested that I explore the ruins of the Daedric shrine Ashurnabitashpi and gather as many historic relics as I can find.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Numani-Rasi of the Urshilaku Ashlander tribe has requested that I explore the ruins of the Daedric shrine Dushariran and gather as many historic relics as I can find.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Numani-Rasi of the Urshilaku Ashlander tribe has requested that I explore the ruins of the Daedric shrine Ashalmawia and gather as many historic relics as I can find.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Jester King Jorunn requested that I steal his bride-to-be away from her minders, so she may join him in his Feast of Fools.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A local crafter, Nesh-Deeka, hopes to establish a trade agreement with Captain Jimila to sell an Argonian musical instrument abroad. He wants me to act as his agent and secure a deal for his vossa-satl.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A faction of bandits in a cavern called Zainsipilu are attempting to grow moon-sugar grass. I've been asked to re-direct their methods through misinformation.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Through unknown breeding and feeding practices, the kwama miners of Matus-Akin have been developing a new, more aggressive breed of kwama. Though this breed needs to be contained, the Temple also wishes to learn more about their breeding methods.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A junior member of the Mages Guild named Skaldir insists that he and his associates have made a significant magical discovery-one that could prove disastrous if left uninvestigated.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Shadow of Sotha Sil, having claimed the Skeleton Key from the Blackfeather Court, is making his way to the center of the Clockwork City-The Cogitum Centralis. Proctor Luciana and I must find some way to follow him.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "According to Gascone, a murder of crows stole a mysterious key from his office in the Clockwork Basilica-the same key that Clavicus Vile and the mysterious shadow cultists seek. I must find this key before the enemy does.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Office of Divine Prosecution suffered a number of casualties to a creature called Graveld in Sil-Var-Woad.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A distraught mother named Lanarie cannot find her son, Arathel. The youth surrendered to the authorities-saying he was part of a plot to kill a Sapiarch. But he disappeared from his cell shortly thereafter. I promised Lanarie I would find her son.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I met a keeper of the Royal Menagerie in Sil-Var-Woad. He warned me that dangerous animals have escaped into the park grounds, but he is searching for a tame indrik that may have escaped during the chaos.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I negotiated an alliance of sorts with Clavicus Vile and Mephala. They agreed to help us get into the Crystal Tower-mostly. Once inside, I need to find a way to stop Nocturnal before she uses the tower to remake reality.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Half-Formed Understandings",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Seeks-the-Dark was hired to steal tokens from a cult within Eton Nir Grotto. Unexpectedly, the cult has been massacred by Daedra who now lurk within. I've been hired to collect the tokens and find Seek-the-Dark's assistant, Erilthel.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Esterdel asked me to find <<1>>, his missing bride-to-be. He tracked her to Archon's Grove, which has been overrun by werewolves. He's hired me to rescue Niralin, or at least collect proof that she's died.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I received a voucher for a special-occasion cake from the renowned master baker, Chef Donolon.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Loremaster Celarus's apprentice, Josajeh, charged me with sealing more time breaches for the Psijic Order-this time in the Iliac Bay region.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A new cluster of time breaches appeared in northeastern Tamriel-specifically the lands of Stonefalls. Eastmarch, and The Rift. As an agent of the Psijic Order, I need to seal them.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Bolu of the Dead-Water tribe, which he calls the Naga-Kur, wants me to go to the Echoing Hollow and accomplish the task he set before me.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Dradeiva, a local Argonian, seeks to prove that the Imperial Ninth Legion disappeared in the Tsofeer Caverns. She hopes to show that her ancestor didn't betray Murkmire. Unfortunately, the caves may also be home to the monstrous voriplasm, Wuju-Ka.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Erilthel has requested that I help save her boss Seeks-the-Dark by completing a gauntlet held by the Blackguards. I'll have to make my way through the many foes of Blackrose Prison and emerge victorious.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Twelve tablets were stolen from the Xinchei-Konu, an ancient Argonian calendar. Jekka-Wass Vozei, the keeper of the calendar, has tasked me to return the first missing tablet.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Hands-That-Heal has lost a wooden box with great sentimental value to him after being attacked by hackwings. He's offered a reward if I successfully return the box to him.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Several envoys from the Root-Whisper Village have gone missing, and Tuwul suspects that Blackguards are the ones responsible.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Several offerings collected by the Root-Whisper tribe have been stolen by the Blackguards. If these offerings aren't recovered, the other tribes will become deeply offended.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The ancient Khajiiti mural known as the Rithana-di-Renada has been completed, but Iraya feels like something is still missing. Legends say the mural emits some kind of music.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "An ancient Khajiiti lich named Arum-Khal threatens to emerge from the depths of the Ashen Scar. If Vastarie and I are to have any hope of stopping him, I'll need to learn more about the monastic order he betrayed: The Order of the Hidden Moon.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A Redguard warrior, Khud af-Hadajja, requested my help in destroying a Daedric device inside a mysterious doomvault before either the servants of Mephala or Mehrunes Dagon get their hands on it.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Cross-cultural Confusion",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "An ancient dro-m'Athra called Zalsheem lurks in the ruins of a Hidden Moon shrine south of Predator Mesa. Her corrupting influence will surely spread if I don't act quickly.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A powerful necromancer named Na'ruzz the Boneweaver lurks in the Bone Pits-a cursed gulch near Orcrest. His dark influence presents a danger to any Khajiit who strays too close.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A good-hearted scoundrel named Daini wants to rob local bandits of their ill-gotten goods. She means to use their wealth to leave Elsweyr with her brother, but seems intent on settling scores before she departs.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A scholar made an ill-advised trek to a guarded temple. Now I must destroy the temple guardian and gather the scholar's scattered notes.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Song of the Sand-Whale",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A traveler from Skyrim named Vigwenn Owl-Watcher claims to have the recipe for a secret concoction that allows the imbiber to see the invisible sand-whales of Elsweyr and hear their haunting song.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Leiborn intends to host a salskap-a bard's gathering to celebrate the recovery of the Bards College instruments. It's sure to be quite a show.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Rigurt the Brash is in Western Skyrim on behalf of the Skald-King. He needs my help to complete his mission.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Gwendis and I discovered a letter from Rada al-Saran to her mentor, Verandis, in a hidden room in Ravenwatch Castle. She asked me to accompany her to investigate the secret island, Grayhome, and the Gray Host castle mentioned in the letter.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Rada al-Saran used the orrery to reach his sanctuary realm in Oblivion, where he will perform the Darkstorm ritual that will destroy the Reach and make the Gray Host truly immortal. To stop him, we must follow him into the Void.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The Dark Heart has awakened and grows more powerful with every beat. While Verandis attempts to deal with Rada al-Saran, I need to go to Markarth and stop Lady Belain from sacrificing the entire city to the Void.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Rada al-Saran is dead and the victims of the Gray Host's assault on Markarth have been restored to life thanks to Verandis.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "An Argonian named Jela asked for my help to rescue her friends from the Sul-Xan, a dangerous tribe that seeks to use them to summon a spirit of destruction using something called the Idol of Xulunaht.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Eveli Sharp-Arrow asked me to accompany her to Gideon as we run down the clue provided by the deciphered Imperial documents and try to find the hidden vault that contains the Four Ambitions.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "An Argonian named Hokatsei claims the Nereid of the ruins of Vunalk, Sister of Pools, turned her brother, Deet-Loh, into a pig. She needs help to return to the ruins and break the spell over her brother.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Legend of the Man-Bull",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I learned that the Minotaur Bhrum-Koska is terrorizing an archeological site in southern Blackwood. I agreed to defeat Bhrum-Koska and remove any unearthed heirlooms that might be drawing Minotaurs to the area.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "The Trophy-Taker",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Xeemhok the Trophy-Taker, a brutal Argonian behemoth, lurks in the ruins near Vunalk. Dozens of brave warriors have challenged him and died. I agreed to take him on, and search the fallen for tokens by which they can be identified.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "The owners of the Happy Averno Shipping Company, Iulius and Scipion Averno, asked for my help dealing with a gang in Blackwood called the Fang-Furls.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Witchmother Taerma asked for my help to defeat a Wraith-of-Crows from the Evergloam called the Crowborne Horror. She tasked me with collecting feathers from vile creatures in order to form an effigy that can bring the creature forth.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "We destroyed an Incarnate at Burning Gyre Keep, but Lyranth believes that the Waking Flame plans to create more. She wants to find the Riven Cataclyst before they do-and she thinks the Bladebearer Dremora can point us to our goal.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Urgarlag Chief-bane of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore Graven Deep.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "A cipher by the name of Meenai-Shai seems to be at the center of a mysterious plot housed within the Sidereal Cloisters.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Bastion Nymic - Glasscrag",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Mercenary Sharp-as-Night needs my help tracking down someone named Reynila Treviri. He thinks Reynila sent rival mercenaries to throw him off her trail. I agreed to help Sharp gather information on Reynila's last known whereabouts.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a note from a trapper named Marcien in the wilderness, along with a snared adolescent guzzard. According to the note, if I deliver the guzzard to Star-Gazer Sariyaah in Ontus, I'll be rewarded.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Bastion Nymic - Fungal Downs",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Wo-Xeeth's Wrath",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "<<1>> told me of dangerous Corelanya relics left in the lair of Wo-Xeeth, an Argonian behemoth changed somehow from the effects of the Writhing Wall. I agreed to dispose of Wo-Xeeth and recover the relics.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Fate-Eater",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I agreed to gather allies and head to the far north of Skingrad to dispatch a Daedra called Stri the Fate-Eater and recover the armaments of the legionaries originally sent to deal with the creature.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Zerith-var received a letter from Cantor Krin'ze asking us to meet with her. Zerith believes it might have something to do with the Rajaska.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I found a note from a trapper named Marcien in the wilderness, along with an old snared guzzard. The note says if I deliver the guzzard to Star-Gazer Sariyaah in Ontus, I'll be rewarded.",
esoQuestData.php:			'name'    => "Self-Preservation",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Zerith's gauntlet beckons him to Khenarthi's Rise, a place that was ruins even in his day. I should help him investigate this unusual summons, as he feels it might relate to our goal to stop Ravith-morna.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Kuzam-jo, a Priest of Mara, asked me to help a struggling theater troupe find the passion they need to perform this Hearts Week.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Kuzam-jo, the Priest of Mara overseeing the Hearts Week holiday festivities, has another task for me. This time I'm to accompany Samara Gautier around Belkarth.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "I pledged myself to the Ruckus faction in the Night Market. My patron, Kharakhal Moon-Eye, wants me to better understand the perils of the districts before sending me out on more jobs for the Ruckus.",
esoQuestData.php:			'journal' => "Kuzam-jo thanked me for the help I offered throughout the Hearts Week festivities. He has one more favor to ask of me.",
